00:00:18.985 --> 00:00:19.986 line:90%
Gu-cheon.

00:00:21.446 --> 00:00:22.697 line:90%
Are you all right?

00:00:23.198 --> 00:00:25.992 line:90%
There was a reason
the Crown Prince's spirit

00:00:26.076 --> 00:00:27.744 line:90%
summoned the pestilent-gwis.

00:00:29.663 --> 00:00:32.457 line:90%
A great calamity
will soon fall upon the entire palace.

00:01:20.672 --> 00:01:24.217 line:90%
Your Majesty, that seat is…

00:01:44.613 --> 00:01:50.285 line:90%
His Majesty's life is in peril.

00:01:50.368 --> 00:01:51.912 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:01:51.995 --> 00:01:56.249 line:90%
-That is not--
-I already know everything.

00:01:58.752 --> 00:02:02.172 line:90%
That the spirit seeks to kill the King.

00:02:03.757 --> 00:02:08.637 line:90%
There is no one but me
who can take this vacant throne.

00:02:09.429 --> 00:02:11.473 line:90%
No one but me.

00:02:12.766 --> 00:02:14.559 line:90%
Only I

00:02:15.060 --> 00:02:20.482 line:90%
can protect this palace
and the royal house!

00:02:20.982 --> 00:02:22.692 line:90%
Only me!

00:02:23.610 --> 00:02:25.236 line:90%
I alone…

00:02:26.446 --> 00:02:30.951 line:90%
I alone can protect them. I alone.

00:02:31.826 --> 00:02:32.911 line:90%
No one but me…

00:02:35.372 --> 00:02:36.581 line:90%
-Councillor!
-Councillor!

00:02:36.665 --> 00:02:38.625 line:90%
-Councillor!
-Left State Councillor!

00:02:39.334 --> 00:02:41.294 line:90%
-Councillor!
-Councillor.

00:02:44.297 --> 00:02:46.091 line:90%
Councillor, are you all right?

00:03:33.013 --> 00:03:38.935 line:90%
THE EAST PALACE

00:03:39.019 --> 00:03:42.814 line:90%
Could the Crown Prince be connected
to what is happening in the palace?

00:03:44.441 --> 00:03:45.442 line:90%
Gu-cheon?

00:03:46.943 --> 00:03:47.902 line:90%
Gu-cheon.

00:03:51.281 --> 00:03:53.033 line:90%
What did you just say?

00:03:54.451 --> 00:03:58.121 line:90%
Something is not right in the palace,
but you do not look well either.

00:04:01.750 --> 00:04:04.252 line:90%
It is because the Crown Prince's spirit
has grown stronger.

00:04:06.755 --> 00:04:09.883 line:90%
That is why I will seal him here.

00:04:09.966 --> 00:04:12.635 line:90%
Seal him? Instead of sending his soul
to the afterlife?

00:04:12.719 --> 00:04:14.637 line:90%
Impossible.
He devoured the pestilent-gwis.

00:04:14.721 --> 00:04:17.265 line:90%
Their souls are now tangled with his.

00:04:19.392 --> 00:04:20.810 line:90%
Good grief.

00:04:21.394 --> 00:04:23.813 line:90%
Do not look at me
as though I am about to die.

00:04:27.233 --> 00:04:29.194 line:90%
And stop frowning. You look ugly.

00:04:29.277 --> 00:04:32.197 line:90%
You have not looked well
since you acquired the gwi-mae's eyes.

00:04:33.990 --> 00:04:35.450 line:90%
Like the gwi-mae from the well…

00:04:35.533 --> 00:04:39.204 line:90%
Are you afraid I might lose my mind
and kill someone?

00:04:43.166 --> 00:04:44.501 line:90%
That will not happen.

00:04:45.543 --> 00:04:49.798 line:90%
Sealing a spirit is a hundred times easier
than destroying it.

00:04:49.881 --> 00:04:52.008 line:90%
Sealing him away will do.

00:04:53.968 --> 00:04:55.386 line:90%
It will work, will it not?

00:04:55.970 --> 00:04:58.223 line:90%
The appeasement rite
will be of great help.

00:05:00.809 --> 00:05:03.103 line:90%
If we soothe the souls
of the pestilent-gwis,

00:05:03.603 --> 00:05:05.730 line:90%
we can weaken the Crown Prince's spirit.

00:05:08.149 --> 00:05:10.235 line:90%
I will walk you back to your quarters.

00:05:10.318 --> 00:05:12.237 line:90%
No need. It is not like I am ill.

00:05:17.033 --> 00:05:18.576 line:90%
But you are.

00:05:23.748 --> 00:05:27.335 line:90%
It will all be over by tonight.

00:05:27.919 --> 00:05:30.880 line:90%
That is right. Sink or swim.

00:05:33.466 --> 00:05:36.553 line:90%
What will you do after this is over
and you leave the palace?

00:05:38.054 --> 00:05:42.016 line:90%
I will drink myself senseless
and sleep for days.

00:05:42.767 --> 00:05:44.227 line:90%
That is not what I mean.

00:05:45.270 --> 00:05:46.813 line:90%
How do you wish to live?

00:05:47.438 --> 00:05:49.315 line:90%
And what do you wish to do with your life?

00:05:51.818 --> 00:05:53.486 line:90%
I have never thought about it.

00:05:54.362 --> 00:05:56.114 line:90%
But I will return to the temple.

00:05:56.990 --> 00:06:00.160 line:90%
What? You said you hated the head monk,

00:06:00.243 --> 00:06:01.911 line:90%
and yet you are going back?

00:06:02.662 --> 00:06:03.663 line:90%
You see,

00:06:04.372 --> 00:06:06.916 line:90%
about four <i>Ri </i>southeast of the temple,

00:06:07.417 --> 00:06:10.253 line:90%
there is a river
running along a sheer cliff.

00:06:11.337 --> 00:06:12.630 line:90%
And that is…

00:06:14.841 --> 00:06:16.926 line:90%
where my mother died.

00:06:20.096 --> 00:06:22.807 line:90%
So even in death,
I cannot leave the temple.

00:06:27.604 --> 00:06:28.855 line:90%
I am sorry.

00:06:34.402 --> 00:06:36.696 line:90%
I dragged you
into the matter of the palace spirit.

00:06:38.156 --> 00:06:41.367 line:90%
-You have nothing to do--
-You have already used me all you wanted.

00:06:41.451 --> 00:06:42.660 line:90%
It is a bit late for that.

00:06:44.120 --> 00:06:48.374 line:90%
You still choose only harsh words,
even at the very end.

00:06:48.958 --> 00:06:51.252 line:90%
I finally found the courage
to be honest with you.

00:06:53.171 --> 00:06:57.717 line:90%
Tonight, you will die.

00:06:58.885 --> 00:07:01.596 line:90%
The one who failed to die with his mother.

00:07:02.639 --> 00:07:05.391 line:90%
The one who was never meant to live,

00:07:05.975 --> 00:07:10.230 line:90%
neither human nor spirit.

00:07:12.315 --> 00:07:15.985 line:90%
Tonight, you will die.

00:07:16.569 --> 00:07:19.530 line:90%
The one who failed to die with his mother.

00:07:19.614 --> 00:07:21.908 line:90%
The one who was never meant to live,

00:07:23.701 --> 00:07:29.624 line:90%
neither human nor spirit.

00:07:30.500 --> 00:07:33.211 line:90%
You will die.

00:07:34.963 --> 00:07:37.674 line:90%
What did Gosuyeochil say, Princess?

00:07:41.678 --> 00:07:48.268 line:90%
<i>Turtle, Turtle</i>

00:07:48.768 --> 00:07:54.357 line:90%
<i>Poke your head out</i>

00:07:54.941 --> 00:08:00.113 line:90%
<i>If you do not</i>

00:08:00.613 --> 00:08:06.160 line:90%
<i>I will roast you and eat you up</i>

00:08:06.661 --> 00:08:08.079 line:90%
Is it nearly ready?

00:08:08.830 --> 00:08:11.291 line:90%
The ritual will begin soon,
at the Hour of the Ox.

00:08:11.916 --> 00:08:13.251 line:90%
It is almost done.

00:08:33.271 --> 00:08:34.981 line:90%
I have given it some thought.

00:08:37.483 --> 00:08:39.986 line:90%
I will go with you to the Realm of Gwi.

00:08:44.699 --> 00:08:46.909 line:90%
I have told you time and again

00:08:47.535 --> 00:08:49.704 line:90%
that you will not last there.

00:08:50.663 --> 00:08:52.373 line:90%
Do not even consider it.

00:09:02.300 --> 00:09:03.509 line:90%
It is all set.

00:09:05.261 --> 00:09:06.387 line:90%
I am heading out.

00:09:06.888 --> 00:09:08.306 line:90%
Wait a moment.

00:09:14.937 --> 00:09:16.064 line:90%
Drink this.

00:09:16.939 --> 00:09:18.900 line:90%
This medicine will replenish
your yang energy.

00:09:18.983 --> 00:09:20.443 line:90%
It is made with rare ingredients.

00:09:22.487 --> 00:09:25.198 line:90%
Well, you should not have…

00:09:29.535 --> 00:09:32.330 line:90%
You should have given it to me sooner.

00:09:35.083 --> 00:09:36.501 line:90%
It is so bitter.

00:09:39.379 --> 00:09:41.464 line:90%
Is there anything I can help you with?

00:09:45.385 --> 00:09:46.511 line:90%
No.

00:09:48.388 --> 00:09:49.389 line:90%
Princess.

00:09:49.889 --> 00:09:52.558 line:90%
The Crown Prince's spirit
is after you as well,

00:09:54.477 --> 00:09:56.187 line:90%
so keep yourself well hidden.

00:10:06.614 --> 00:10:07.615 line:90%
What is the matter?

00:10:10.535 --> 00:10:11.994 line:90%
Before coming here,

00:10:13.246 --> 00:10:15.581 line:90%
I visited my grandmother's quarters.

00:10:15.665 --> 00:10:16.999 line:90%
Why did you go there?

00:10:17.792 --> 00:10:19.669 line:90%
You treat her like an enemy…

00:10:38.521 --> 00:10:40.940 line:90%
You will not wake for half a day.

00:10:48.322 --> 00:10:49.157 line:90%
Why?

00:10:50.741 --> 00:10:53.327 line:90%
-Why…
-I do not know myself.

00:10:53.828 --> 00:10:57.206 line:90%
The moment I heard the gwi-mae say
that you would die tonight,

00:10:57.290 --> 00:10:59.459 line:90%
I moved before I could even think.

00:11:06.299 --> 00:11:09.177 line:90%
You are the only one in this palace
I can trust and rely on.

00:11:09.760 --> 00:11:10.803 line:90%
So…

00:11:13.473 --> 00:11:15.641 line:90%
I will not stand by and let you die.

00:11:20.855 --> 00:11:22.815 line:90%
I will save you

00:11:24.108 --> 00:11:25.943 line:90%
even if it means sacrificing my life.

00:11:41.501 --> 00:11:44.003 line:90%
Thank you for protecting me all this time.

00:11:52.011 --> 00:11:53.930 line:90%
From this moment forward,

00:11:55.306 --> 00:11:57.350 line:90%
I will take over your duties.

00:12:23.501 --> 00:12:25.753 line:90%
The appeasement rite will begin soon.

00:12:26.254 --> 00:12:29.090 line:90%
It seems the shaman has a clever plan.

00:13:27.523 --> 00:13:28.524 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:13:29.275 --> 00:13:31.068 line:90%
Do not make a scene.

00:13:49.629 --> 00:13:51.797 line:90%
The Crown Prince is here.

00:15:00.282 --> 00:15:03.035 line:90%
So, you have become an ak-gwi after all.

00:15:04.745 --> 00:15:06.372 line:90%
Do not even think of interfering.

00:15:07.623 --> 00:15:09.375 line:90%
You must feel wronged and resentful.

00:15:10.501 --> 00:15:12.002 line:90%
I understand that as well.

00:15:13.421 --> 00:15:16.132 line:90%
You were killed by your own father,
so it is only natural.

00:15:20.803 --> 00:15:21.679 line:90%
Brother!

00:15:26.142 --> 00:15:28.811 line:90%
He abandoned me because I could hear
the voices of the dead,

00:15:30.020 --> 00:15:32.231 line:90%
and he let my mother die.

00:15:32.314 --> 00:15:35.067 line:90%
I despise Father as well. Brother!

00:15:43.242 --> 00:15:45.327 line:90%
I told you not to interfere.

00:19:03.025 --> 00:19:04.985 line:90%
<i>I will not stand by and let you die.</i>

00:19:06.779 --> 00:19:08.781 line:90%
<i>Even if it means sacrificing my life.</i>

00:19:42.940 --> 00:19:44.775 line:90%
Are you telling me not to do it?

00:19:55.577 --> 00:19:58.372 line:90%
This is the only way to save the Princess.

00:20:03.168 --> 00:20:05.129 line:90%
She was willing to risk her life for me,

00:20:06.672 --> 00:20:08.090 line:90%
so I must do the same.

00:21:09.985 --> 00:21:11.487 line:90%
<i>Humans.</i>

00:21:12.529 --> 00:21:16.825 line:90%
<i>They move toward death</i>
<i>from the moment they are born.</i>

00:21:18.911 --> 00:21:20.829 line:90%
<i>One's status</i>

00:21:21.705 --> 00:21:23.874 line:90%
<i>or character</i>

00:21:24.833 --> 00:21:26.460 line:90%
<i>does not matter.</i>

00:21:30.923 --> 00:21:34.843 line:90%
<i>In the end, death comes equally to all,</i>

00:21:36.053 --> 00:21:37.679 line:90%
<i>so there is no need to grieve</i>

00:21:38.388 --> 00:21:40.557 line:90%
<i>or feel wronged.</i>

00:23:00.637 --> 00:23:03.348 line:90%
No wonder the palace is thick
with Yin energy.

00:23:04.641 --> 00:23:06.185 line:90%
So it was you.

00:23:07.352 --> 00:23:08.854 line:90%
Primordial Gwi-mae.

00:23:12.107 --> 00:23:13.442 line:90%
I will give you

00:23:14.067 --> 00:23:15.944 line:90%
whatever you want.

00:23:16.445 --> 00:23:17.487 line:90%
In return,

00:23:18.864 --> 00:23:20.657 line:90%
grant me your power

00:23:22.326 --> 00:23:24.077 line:90%
so that I can save the Princess.

00:27:18.061 --> 00:27:21.648 line:90%
How much longer, Your Majesty?

00:27:38.457 --> 00:27:40.959 line:90%
<i>To stop the pestilence,</i>

00:27:42.127 --> 00:27:46.256 line:90%
<i>I first placed you, the powerless,</i>
<i>before the blade.</i>

00:27:47.382 --> 00:27:50.010 line:90%
<i>Without asking your leave,</i>

00:27:50.927 --> 00:27:52.679 line:90%
<i>I shattered your fates.</i>

00:27:55.557 --> 00:27:58.560 line:90%
<i>And yet, I was unable to stop anything.</i>

00:27:59.352 --> 00:28:03.899 line:90%
<i>All I hear are your resentful wails.</i>

00:28:09.196 --> 00:28:11.615 line:90%
This is a sin that can never…

00:28:15.285 --> 00:28:16.453 line:90%
be washed away.

00:28:19.122 --> 00:28:22.125 line:90%
<i>I do not mean to seek forgiveness.</i>

00:28:23.835 --> 00:28:25.879 line:90%
If you wish…

00:28:29.799 --> 00:28:32.093 line:90%
you may take my life at once.

00:28:36.264 --> 00:28:38.600 line:90%
<i>Yet if my life is spared,</i>

00:28:40.060 --> 00:28:42.771 line:90%
<i>I shall embrace those</i>
<i>left behind by your deaths.</i>

00:28:44.022 --> 00:28:45.023 line:90%
<i>Your parents,</i>

00:28:45.982 --> 00:28:47.025 line:90%
<i>siblings,</i>

00:28:48.235 --> 00:28:49.236 line:90%
<i>children,</i>

00:28:49.736 --> 00:28:51.738 line:90%
and all your kin.

00:28:54.282 --> 00:28:56.368 line:90%
I shall care for them until the very end…

00:29:01.081 --> 00:29:04.584 line:90%
as the parent of this nation.

00:29:12.968 --> 00:29:16.096 line:90%
<i>And for this sin</i>
<i>I could not pay for in this life,</i>

00:29:17.514 --> 00:29:20.559 line:90%
I shall answer for it
again and again in the afterlife.

00:29:23.895 --> 00:29:26.273 line:90%
So let go of your lingering resentment…

00:29:30.068 --> 00:29:31.820 line:90%
and move on to the afterlife.

00:29:35.240 --> 00:29:37.534 line:90%
<i>Now lay down that heavy burden</i>

00:29:39.411 --> 00:29:41.413 line:90%
<i>here in this world…</i>

00:29:44.583 --> 00:29:46.126 line:90%
<i>and pass on…</i>

00:29:49.838 --> 00:29:51.464 line:90%
<i>to the other side.</i>

00:30:34.299 --> 00:30:38.720 line:90%
I have been waiting
for the pestilent-gwis to leave.

00:31:53.086 --> 00:31:54.295 line:90%
It cannot…

00:31:56.172 --> 00:31:58.425 line:90%
It cannot end like this.

00:32:11.146 --> 00:32:13.273 line:90%
Do you wish to kill your father that much?

00:32:15.233 --> 00:32:16.735 line:90%
You see…

00:32:19.237 --> 00:32:22.490 line:90%
I have been tormented all my life,
believing that I killed my mother.

00:32:23.825 --> 00:32:25.785 line:90%
Fearing that sin would turn me
into an ak-gwi,

00:32:25.869 --> 00:32:29.748 line:90%
I have forced myself to live on
so that I would not become like you.

00:32:31.124 --> 00:32:34.878 line:90%
But why would you go so far
as to become an ak-gwi…

00:32:57.442 --> 00:32:59.652 line:90%
I wanted to be King.

00:33:01.362 --> 00:33:04.073 line:90%
But none of that matters now.

00:33:05.074 --> 00:33:08.328 line:90%
This palace, where I cannot become King.

00:33:09.704 --> 00:33:11.706 line:90%
Those lowly subjects.

00:33:15.084 --> 00:33:16.503 line:90%
Those within the palace…

00:33:20.089 --> 00:33:22.801 line:90%
and those beyond its walls…

00:33:25.011 --> 00:33:26.763 line:90%
I will kill them all.

00:33:30.934 --> 00:33:34.395 line:90%
Destroying your soul was the one thing
I wished to avoid.

00:33:35.188 --> 00:33:37.565 line:90%
You cannot destroy me.

00:33:38.274 --> 00:33:40.318 line:90%
If you destroy someone's soul,

00:33:40.401 --> 00:33:44.030 line:90%
you will, in turn,
become an ak-gwi as well.

00:33:54.958 --> 00:33:56.459 line:90%
I know.

00:33:57.377 --> 00:33:59.420 line:90%
But if I do not kill you,

00:33:59.504 --> 00:34:01.673 line:90%
the curse will not be broken,
and the Princess will die.

00:34:03.299 --> 00:34:06.052 line:90%
From the moment I met Primordial Gwi-mae,

00:34:06.553 --> 00:34:08.638 line:90%
I was prepared to become an ak-gwi!

00:35:03.860 --> 00:35:05.695 line:90%
It is all over.

00:35:26.883 --> 00:35:29.010 line:90%
Councillor!

00:35:46.778 --> 00:35:47.820 line:90%
Chief Eunuch Kim!

00:35:51.407 --> 00:35:52.450 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:36:05.588 --> 00:36:07.298 line:90%
Gu-cheon!

00:37:18.619 --> 00:37:21.456 line:90%
I will give you all the yang energy
I have left…

00:37:28.212 --> 00:37:29.672 line:90%
so go back.

00:38:26.562 --> 00:38:28.106 line:90%
Gu-cheon, please wake up.

00:38:28.689 --> 00:38:29.690 line:90%
Gu-cheon.

00:38:44.080 --> 00:38:46.958 line:90%
Take my yang energy.

00:38:50.461 --> 00:38:52.672 line:90%
You cannot die like this.

00:38:53.297 --> 00:38:54.924 line:90%
I will not let you go.

00:38:56.092 --> 00:38:57.093 line:90%
No.

00:38:59.220 --> 00:39:00.138 line:90%
No.

00:39:02.390 --> 00:39:03.432 line:90%
Gu-cheon.

00:39:10.523 --> 00:39:12.316 line:90%
That is enough.

00:39:30.209 --> 00:39:32.044 line:90%
Now that it has come to this,

00:39:32.712 --> 00:39:34.881 line:90%
let us go all out.

00:39:35.381 --> 00:39:37.008 line:90%
I have already become an ak-gwi.

00:39:37.091 --> 00:39:39.468 line:90%
Rather than let a gwi-mae devour my soul…

00:40:01.073 --> 00:40:01.949 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:40:02.450 --> 00:40:05.786 line:90%
There have been no further reports
of the pestilence.

00:40:06.287 --> 00:40:08.706 line:90%
The rites in each region
concluded without issue,

00:40:08.789 --> 00:40:12.418 line:90%
and the unrest among the people
is settling.

00:40:12.919 --> 00:40:14.670 line:90%
Very well.

00:40:15.463 --> 00:40:17.089 line:90%
You may leave.

00:40:24.555 --> 00:40:25.640 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:40:27.266 --> 00:40:30.144 line:90%
All the strange calamities in the palace
over the past few days

00:40:31.020 --> 00:40:32.813 line:90%
have ceased.

00:40:46.410 --> 00:40:47.536 line:90%
Let us go.

00:40:59.882 --> 00:41:00.800 line:90%
<i>However,</i>

00:41:02.760 --> 00:41:05.012 line:90%
<i>the Queen Dowager,</i>
<i>now at her private residence,</i>

00:41:06.097 --> 00:41:08.307 line:90%
<i>is not of sound mind.</i>

00:41:16.232 --> 00:41:18.526 line:90%
<i>How is Prince Iksang?</i>

00:41:23.572 --> 00:41:25.241 line:90%
<i>He is under secret investigation</i>

00:41:26.325 --> 00:41:31.163 line:90%
<i>for summoning a shaman</i>
<i>to perform rites against Your Majesty.</i>

00:41:34.166 --> 00:41:35.459 line:90%
Very well.

00:41:36.377 --> 00:41:37.753 line:90%
You may leave.

00:41:39.422 --> 00:41:41.090 line:90%
It has been three days.

00:41:50.641 --> 00:41:51.851 line:90%
Princess.

00:41:54.937 --> 00:41:58.107 line:90%
Perhaps it is time to give up on him.

00:42:02.903 --> 00:42:05.072 line:90%
We thought he was dead last time,

00:42:06.157 --> 00:42:07.700 line:90%
and yet he woke up, did he not?

00:42:08.200 --> 00:42:10.494 line:90%
Even for Gu-cheon…

00:42:13.789 --> 00:42:14.915 line:90%
Everyone is saying

00:42:15.833 --> 00:42:18.461 line:90%
that he is dead.

00:42:20.921 --> 00:42:22.465 line:90%
Do not cry.

00:42:24.884 --> 00:42:25.801 line:90%
He is not dead.

00:42:40.107 --> 00:42:41.192 line:90%
Look.

00:42:43.694 --> 00:42:44.904 line:90%
The child is crying.

00:42:46.739 --> 00:42:50.409 line:90%
So please stop troubling us any further
and return now.

00:42:56.832 --> 00:42:59.001 line:90%
If you cannot find your way back…

00:43:01.295 --> 00:43:04.924 line:90%
then ring the bell so that I may find you.

00:43:24.318 --> 00:43:25.736 line:90%
Ggeomeoksali.

00:43:26.362 --> 00:43:29.990 line:90%
That one is called Ggeomeoksali.
It is no ordinary creature.

00:43:30.074 --> 00:43:33.285 line:90%
It attaches to the living, not places,
feeding on yang energy.

00:43:33.994 --> 00:43:35.287 line:90%
The living…

00:43:39.208 --> 00:43:40.751 line:90%
He is alive.

00:43:55.349 --> 00:43:57.852 line:90%
<i>About four </i>ri <i>southeast of the temple,</i>

00:43:58.352 --> 00:44:00.938 line:90%
<i>there is a river</i>
<i>running along a sheer cliff.</i>

00:44:04.024 --> 00:44:05.234 line:90%
<i>And that is</i>

00:44:05.985 --> 00:44:08.320 line:90%
<i>where my mother died.</i>

00:44:09.572 --> 00:44:12.450 line:90%
<i>So even in death,</i>
<i>I cannot leave the temple.</i>

00:44:27.590 --> 00:44:28.591 line:90%
Please…

00:44:52.990 --> 00:44:54.575 line:90%
I knew you would be here.

00:45:04.376 --> 00:45:05.920 line:90%
It is all over.

00:45:09.215 --> 00:45:11.383 line:90%
You can now leave the palace

00:45:13.177 --> 00:45:14.803 line:90%
as you wished.

00:45:15.638 --> 00:45:16.722 line:90%
So

00:45:18.307 --> 00:45:20.017 line:90%
do not stay here alone

00:45:21.936 --> 00:45:23.604 line:90%
and come back with me.

00:45:26.023 --> 00:45:29.193 line:90%
You said you were living without purpose,
just existing.

00:45:29.693 --> 00:45:30.653 line:90%
But live on.

00:45:32.988 --> 00:45:35.282 line:90%
You may still live like a spirit.

00:45:37.117 --> 00:45:38.035 line:90%
But live on!

00:45:41.789 --> 00:45:43.791 line:90%
Are you listening to me?

00:46:15.197 --> 00:46:18.450 line:90%
You said that your own life mattered
more than anything, did you not?

00:46:20.786 --> 00:46:23.247 line:90%
Did you think I would be glad…

00:46:25.958 --> 00:46:28.002 line:90%
if you threw your life away to save me?

00:46:47.021 --> 00:46:48.272 line:90%
You wretch.

00:46:50.107 --> 00:46:53.527 line:90%
Come back at once
before I drag you out myself!

00:47:45.954 --> 00:47:47.122 line:90%
Princess.

00:48:26.078 --> 00:48:27.079 line:90%
Good grief.

00:48:33.001 --> 00:48:34.420 line:90%
So noisy.

00:48:40.050 --> 00:48:41.343 line:90%
You are crying again.

00:49:30.684 --> 00:49:32.519 line:90%
You made it back.

00:49:35.272 --> 00:49:37.357 line:90%
Have you made all your preparations
to leave?

00:49:38.025 --> 00:49:39.318 line:90%
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:49:42.112 --> 00:49:43.238 line:90%
However,

00:49:44.948 --> 00:49:46.992 line:90%
this is quite a grand send-off.

00:49:51.079 --> 00:49:55.000 line:90%
So you do not intend to let me go
so easily, do you?

00:49:55.501 --> 00:49:58.378 line:90%
I know what you went through…

00:50:00.589 --> 00:50:03.050 line:90%
in secret here.

00:50:03.133 --> 00:50:04.468 line:90%
And you know

00:50:06.053 --> 00:50:08.597 line:90%
far too much about the palace
and about me…

00:50:11.767 --> 00:50:14.186 line:90%
do you not?

00:50:20.400 --> 00:50:21.360 line:90%
Rise.

00:50:26.615 --> 00:50:28.742 line:90%
People change

00:50:30.327 --> 00:50:31.912 line:90%
once they get what they want.

00:50:33.330 --> 00:50:36.291 line:90%
Your promise meant little, Your Majesty.

00:50:50.848 --> 00:50:52.724 line:90%
Are you seeing something again?

00:50:55.477 --> 00:50:56.645 line:90%
The spirits of past Kings

00:50:58.105 --> 00:51:02.484 line:90%
and the countless Princes
who never became King linger here.

00:51:20.627 --> 00:51:22.087 line:90%
You may leave now.

00:51:22.170 --> 00:51:24.256 line:90%
Are you sparing me?

00:51:31.763 --> 00:51:33.473 line:90%
We shall see.

00:51:56.538 --> 00:52:00.250 line:90%
He would not suddenly change his mind
and kill me, would he?

00:52:04.463 --> 00:52:05.589 line:90%
Good grief.

00:52:13.722 --> 00:52:15.223 line:90%
Why are you still standing there?

00:52:20.646 --> 00:52:22.606 line:90%
Have you grown attached to the palace?

00:52:25.192 --> 00:52:26.318 line:90%
Are you going somewhere?

00:52:27.569 --> 00:52:29.071 line:90%
I am coming with you.

00:52:29.154 --> 00:52:30.113 line:90%
What?

00:52:31.198 --> 00:52:32.074 line:90%
Why?

00:52:41.041 --> 00:52:44.127 line:90%
You went out of your way
to help me settle my affairs.

00:52:45.545 --> 00:52:47.464 line:90%
Now it is my turn to help you.

00:52:49.132 --> 00:52:50.050 line:90%
Goodness.

00:52:56.431 --> 00:52:57.891 line:90%
It will not be easy.

00:52:59.393 --> 00:53:01.770 line:90%
Do not whine to me later
about how hard it is.

00:53:07.401 --> 00:53:08.443 line:90%
Let us go.

00:53:11.989 --> 00:53:12.823 line:90%
Goodness.

00:53:50.110 --> 00:53:55.032 line:90%
THE EAST PALACE

00:56:51.917 --> 00:56:55.170 line:90%
Subtitle translation by: Yun-hee Jang